import React, {useState} from 'react' import './AddUser.css' import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom' const AddUser = () => { const [name, setName] = useState('') const [email, setEmail] = useState('') const [address, setAddress] = useState('') const navigate = useNavigate() return (
setName(e.target.value)} value = {name} />
setEmail(e.target.value)} value = {email} />
setAddress(e.target.value)} value = {address} />
) } export default AddUser
